I want to create a simple and nice-looking quiz website Main function: Allow students to select out of few topics max of 4 topics and when they select, they can start a quiz that has a timer and when they are done, they get their result in form of a pie chart showing each topic scores then a total score bellow it, then they can choose to restart And some other cool functionalities for students How can I go about it I want to use react with Javascript, I want it simple as well as smart and cool animations using various react libraries

